Don't hate me.
I got a new Livejournal.
This is my 3rd ever since junior high.

Obnoxious? Maybe. However..
I feel like I'm on the road to making a new life for myself, with a whole new outlook and a whole new attitude. I'm leaving everything behind except my heart and the good memories. Goodbye old world. Goodbye old me.
